org.sensorhub.impl.service.sos

Class StorageDataProviderFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sensorhub.impl.service.sos.StorageDataProviderFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDataProviderFactory, ISOSDataProviderFactory
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    StreamWithStorageProviderFactory

    public class StorageDataProviderFactory
extends Object
implements IDataProviderFactory

    Factory for storage data providers.

    This factory is associated to an SOS offering and is persistent throughout the lifetime of the service, so it must be threadsafe.

    However, the server will obtain a new data provider instance from this factory for each incoming request so the providers themselves don't need to be threadsafe.

    Since:
    Sep 15, 2013
    Author:
    Alex Robin
